{"tid":1650522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"藍絲都醒撚過你班傻鳩，我決定投誠898","createTime":"2019-10-13T04:12:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T04:53:01.000Z","uid":105678,"like":8,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"44987a5f834117f5863980187b2bd76043040bca","tid":1650522,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:12:53.000Z","msg":"人地藍絲做埋啲低b嘢都唔會割，你地黃屍切個蛋糕就可以由尋晚嘈到依加<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第時容乜易講錯幾句就係連登畀人割蓆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我決定考警入去做紀律部隊了，錢又多又冇藍絲捧，又有得吊大陸長腿<br />\n<br />\n仲使能係度同你班傻鳩黃絲奶美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b00d49c283cbf8ef664dc94b27594e2466fb1d4","tid":1650522,"uid":2676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:13:07.000Z","msg":"Block"},{"pid":"c1b530e20ad418a4d12f8788157660a8140829b4","tid":1650522,"uid":216888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:13:18.000Z","msg":"成件事原本唔好再提係最好解決方法 不分化 <br />\n相信將來唔會見到同類事情發生<br />\n<br />\n唔好再提比人拎黎當新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我屌成個連登都生日post 你同佢地有咩分別<br />\n<br />\n起底報警個班一係藍絲 一係唔撚用腦 比晒子彈人<br />\n<br />\n到時popo可能再更加濫權拉街上做緊任何野既人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><br />\n成功因爲生日而控入罪之後法庭可以有案例更易入其他手足罪<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔可以比晒子彈對方去執行惡法 間接承認條條例<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老帽 報警個個仲撚on9過生日個班 屌你醒下啦 用下個腦啦"},{"pid":"8fd0a1bbd47c5ffe77827ff88cafbec272995b0d","tid":1650522,"uid":312692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T04:13:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KnAJUrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKnAJUrV.jpg&h=222a48c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>10.13 10.14 不見不散</strong></span></span>"},{"